14 | Incomplete ralph/ deletion, broken stats.ts path | done |\n327\t| 1-3-workflow-state-module | 74 | Naming collision, validation gaps | done |\n328\t| **Epic Total** | **~307** | 8 issues found by review | **DONE** |\n329\t\n330\tEpic 1 achieved its goal: remove legacy subsystems (beads, ralph, legacy verification) and establish the first v2 module (workflow-state). The codebase is cleaner (-656K LOC from ralph alone) and ready for Epic 2.\n331\t\n332\t---\n333\t\n334\t# Session Retrospective — 2026-04-02 (Session 3: Story 2-1 + Full-Day Rollup)\n335\t\n336\t**Generated:** 2026-04-02T15:05 UTC\n337\t\n338\t## 1. Session Summary\n339\t\n340\t**Date:** 2026-04-02\n341\t**Stories attempted this session:** 1\n342\t**Stories completed this session:** 1\n343\t**Full-day stories completed:** 4 (1-1, 1-2, 1-3, 2-1)\n344\t\n345\t| Story | Phases Run | Outcome | Notes |\n346\t|-------|-----------|---------|-------|\n347\t| 2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema | create-story, dev-story, code-review, verification | done | First Epic 2 story; JSON Schema + ajv validation |\n348\t\n349\t**Sprint progress after session:** Epic 1 fully done (3/3). Epic 2 started — story 2-1 done, 2-2 through 2-5 remain in backlog.\n350\t\n351\t---\n352\t\n353\t## 2. Issues Analysis\n354\t\n355\t### Issues from Story 2-1 (from .session-issues.md)\n356\t\n357\t**Spec/Config Gaps (3)**\n358\t- `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` does not exist — create-story agent inferred config from file locations.\n359\t- Technical workflow engine research document referenced in epics-v2.md does not exist locally.\n360\t- Implementation artifact paths inferred, not read from a config source.\n361\t\n362\t**Code Quality Issues Found by Review (2)**\n363\t- **HIGH (fixed):** Branch coverage 75% on `schema-validate.ts` — `??` fallback paths in error mapping never tested. Review added 4 fake validator tests to reach 100% branch coverage.\n364\t- **MEDIUM (fixed):** `require()` calls in ESM test file — replaced with fake validator pattern.\n365\t\n366\t**Deferred Items (2)**\n367\t- **LOW:** No barrel re-export for `schema-validate.ts` — downstream imports directly. Not blocking.\n368\t- **LOW:** Module-level Ajv singleton pays compilation cost at import time. Negligible for CLI usage.\n369\t\n370\t**Naming Deviation (1)**\n371\t- Story spec said `validateWorkflowYaml` but dev used `validateWorkflowSchema` — function validates parsed JS objects, not YAML strings. Pragmatically correct but diverges from spec.\n372\t\n373\t**ajv Dependency Decision (1)**\n374\t- Story spec said dev-time cost, but validation runs at CLI runtime (story 2-5 `validate` command), so `ajv` was correctly added as a production dependency.\n375\t\n376\t**Verification Format Problems (1)**\n377\t- Proof document required 3 rewrites: wrong headers (`### AC` instead of `## AC`), then missing evidence format (needs `bash`+`output` code blocks), then finally correct. This is the same format issue seen in Sessions 1 and 2 — it remains unfixed in subagent instructions.\n378\t\n379\t### Severity Distribution\n380\t\n381\t| Severity | Count | Fixed? |\n382\t|----------|-------|--------|\n383\t| HIGH | 1 | Yes (branch coverage) |\n384\t| MEDIUM | 1 | Yes (ESM require) |\n385\t| LOW | 3 | Deferred |\n386\t\n387\t---\n388\t\n389\t## 3. Cost Analysis\n390\t\n391\t### This Session (Story 2-1 + orchestrator overhead)\n392\t\n393\tFrom `codeharness stats --save`:\n394\t\n395\t**Total cost: $15.37** across 119 API calls (covers stories 2-1 and 1-3 in current tracking window).\n396\t\n397\t**Cost by Phase:**\n398\t\n399\t| Phase | Calls | Cost | % of Total |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018KGgogVCKrkpaQRviEJXhG","session_id":"5fca15c0-771e-463c-9e4f-c528b230e359","uuid":"1a98fd1f-eaae-4545-975c-3f5af1462459","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:07:44.214Z"}
